## Rooms

### Basic Room
```typescript
const kitchen = EntityTemplates.room(
  'Kitchen',
  'A well-equipped kitchen with modern appliances.'
);
```

### Dark Room
```typescript
const cellar = buildEntity('cellar')
  .asRoom({ darkByDefault: true })
  .withIdentity('Cellar', 'A damp, musty cellar. It\'s very dark here.')
  .build();
```

### Outdoor Location
```typescript
const garden = buildEntity('garden')
  .asRoom()
  .withIdentity('Garden', 'A beautiful garden with colorful flowers.')
  .withTrait(new OutdoorTrait())  // Custom trait for weather effects
  .build();
```

### Room with Custom Capacity
```typescript
const closet = buildEntity('closet')
  .withIdentity('Closet', 'A small storage closet.')
  .asRoom()
  .updateTrait(TraitType.CONTAINER, { capacity: 20 })  // Override default
  .build();
```

## Containers

### Simple Box
